narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I developed my vocal technique, focusing on lip position especially this semester, and beginning my study of singing in French. I learned and studied 3 new pieces and worked on some new vocal exercises.
Circular breathing, posture, finger independence techniques

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Lessons are essential for continued vocal study--I wouldn't change the structure of how lessons are offered.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If you are a musician looking for good quality lessons at Yale, no question--do it!
